ve.org/web/20090616154147/http://www.minniscomms.com.au/educationtoday/articles.php?articleid=12 Movie making project boosts school attendance]\n*[http://www.realtimearts.net/article/issue63/8562 David Vadiveloo: grass roots reconciliation]\n*[http://www.abc.net.au/rn/talks/lm/stories/s1341400.htm Life Matters Feature Interview: David Vadiveloo]\n*[http://www.abc.net.au/rn/talks/lm/stories/s1527871.htm Aboriginal Town Camp School]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20091023210959/http://www.dlux.org.au/codingcultures/handbook.html Coding cultures]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20100802023312/http://www.yirrkala.com/mulka/video.html Mulka Media Centre]\n*<ref>[https://legal.thomsonreuters.com.au/federal-law-reports-set-volumes-1-318/productdetail/33093/ Volume 126 Federal Law Reports at 336]</ref>\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Vadiveloo, David}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Date of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Australian film directors]]\n[[Category:Australian film producers]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Monash Law School alumni]]\n[[Category:University of Melbourne alumni]]\n[[Category:People from Alice Springs]]\n[[Category:Lawyers from Melbourne]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2014}}\n{{Use Australian English|date=May 2018}}\n{{lead too short|date=June 2012}}\n{{Infobox person\n| honorific_prefix          = \n| name                      = David Selvarajah Vadiveloo\n| honorific_suffix          = \n| native_name               = \n| native_name_lang          = \n| image                     = David_Vadiveloo.jpg\n| image_size                = \n| alt                       = \n| caption                   = \n| birth_name                = \n| birth_date                = <!-- {{Birth date and age|df=yes|YYYY|MM|DD}} -->\n| birth_place               = \n| disappeared_date          = <!-- {{Disappeared date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|M